{"tid":58223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"80年代廣西「推普廢粵」宣傳片：成效非常！","createTime":"2016-12-28T15:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-06T16:23:42.000Z","uid":53060,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1eac0ee85d385a885552ca594c8a8b52a37138d0","tid":58223,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:51:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=M38GT5aMumM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DM38GT5aMumM&d=O%2BQ4jgIId%2FvCv6oS1vfW8GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=45658c30\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=M38GT5aMumM</a>"},{"pid":"cd02a3e52c018523c914524b749dc9f1207de83a","tid":58223,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">只需十年，廣西粵語消亡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n廣東當局（主要為北方官）一直否認「推普」會令粵語方言消亡，但歷史早已證明，方言及地方文化若在主流文化（此專指普通話）強勢壓力下，若不能得到適當保謢勢必逐漸消亡。遠且不說，廣西首府南寧方言的消亡便是例證。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">令當地以講白話為恥</span><br />\n<br />\n南寧白話與粵語同源，發音雖有差異但溝通無問題，七、八十年代以前南寧白話無論在官場、廣播電台還是公共場所一律暢通；但自一九九六年開始當局強行「推普」，官方場合只講普通話，電台電視也改普，當局又大事獎勵各行業推普，「以講普通話為榮」；巴士改普令不少老南寧「聽唔明」。<br />\n<br />\n僅僅十多年後，南寧白話即告「危機」，現在南寧街頭全是蹩腳普通話，白話幾近消亡。當地媒體曾以「南寧白話正在『推普』中消失」為題做報道，直言因「推普」越來越多南寧人不講白話，以講白話為恥，幼兒園和學校更杜絕白話，使白話和相關文化消亡，呼籲當局「推普」同時不要排斥本土方言文化；並引廣西民族大學語言學專家指，推普與保護方言，客觀上是矛盾和對立的。"},{"pid":"42eb8268ee753bbce71896d09696c2e0398800d2","tid":58223,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:57:20.000Z","msg":"僅僅十多年後，南寧白話即告「危機」，現在南寧街頭全是蹩腳普通話，白話幾近消亡。<br />\n<br />\n越來越多南寧人不講白話，以講白話為恥，幼兒園和學校更杜絕白話，使白話和相關文化消亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79362579bcd182ed03a7580eb5c1960c9c67d86b","tid":58223,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1d99ef76e6149aae7a99a439f42956f1c604725","tid":58223,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:41:36.000Z","msg":"文明用語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2325521f56a403d758a3b53ce963514cae09b20","tid":58223,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T16:46:40.000Z","msg":"聽倒文明用語真係想嘔"},{"pid":"b7119ed09aa828cd5ba4ab7be46099e89fe5c270","tid":58223,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T23:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文明用語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src