pid":"fa4d78d42cb16618671e2284237ddfac57ee3ec0","tid":58223,"uid":17224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-06T12:59:31.000Z","msg":"唔係個名話 土共講嘅所謂'文明用語'<br />\n就係文明<br />\n<br />\n我覺得真正嘅文明係文化背景唔同<br />\n但係相處唔係反客為主<br />\n<br />\n利申：1999"},{"pid":"01a2fee00c2af8d4ab0f81f7ecf9b22d5764a286","tid":58223,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-06T13:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958da08e9846c1c1db4cc4de463200ac8de039fc","tid":58223,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-06T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"廣東應該好少少, 因珠江口一帶自我保護意識強冇咁易消滅<br />\n加上香港因素又令廣東話既重要性又強返啲<br />\n但咁落去都有危機"},{"pid":"6bec63f0fb2efb1c800b0d763fec1de20ee66af4","tid":58223,"uid":68325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-06T16:11:14.000Z","msg":"廣西以前係粵語為主,同RIP佐好多年應該大家都心知肚明,<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af51d42b1d35f9dab693f86c5ce3f379cf661a92","tid":58223,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-06T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"廣西仲有好多人講白話"},{"pid":"61960d61111ee2f25a0024be98645d158abf46bc","tid":58223,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-06T16:15:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廣西以前係粵語為主,同RIP佐好多年應該大家都心知肚明,<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉晒講文明用語"},{"pid":"d1b3374df33787ce4d1ae638398a07aefdad1223","tid":58223,"uid":9264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-06T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廣東應該好少少, 因珠江口一帶自我保護意識強冇咁易消滅<br />\n加上香港因素又令廣東話既重要性又強返啲<br />\n但咁落去都有危機</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家好多小學中學生講普通話，可能第日你個孫話你死老野講埋哂d鄉下話"}]}